

POST http://localhost:8000/login

Body as form-data in postman:

  user name: nouman@gmail.com
  p a s s w o rd: nouman

response:
{
    "access_token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJub3VtYW5yZWhtYW4wNDJAZ21haWwuY29tIiwiZXhwIjoxNjk3MTMxOTI4fQ.XqK2ASfSUqImooaOd98mvkBmQyhUPj9qpwkAe4sMo0U",
    "token_type": "bearer"
}

*********************************

GET all posts:


GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/posts/?limit=10&skip=0

with bearer token received from login

*********************************

Get post:

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/posts/1

with bearer token received from login

*********************************

Create post

POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/posts

body:

{
  "title": "my post",
  "content": "my content",
  "published": true
}

response:

{
    "title": "my post",
    "content": "my content",
    "published": true,
    "id": 2,
    "created_at": "2024-11-02T18:23:47.405932+05:00",
    "owner_id": 1,
    "owner": {
        "id": 1,
        "email": "nouman@gmail.com",
        "created_at": "2024-10-16T19:22:42.527891+05:00"
    }
}

*********************************


*********************************

Create vote

POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/vote

body:
{
    "post_id": 1,
    "dir": 1
}

response:

{
    "message": "successfully added vote"
}

*********************************